  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1ffb2123&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHytN6OfQHzVlsbs8iaISlcZXZOzpHLb0SZyyCDfjiaKkrl1VKvJgjQB0oL7D3lib2x3d8ERkIY4oY1fJbibDpCI3xQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"105183\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 10px auto;text-align: left;\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/voc/Guide\">\n    <div style=\"border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(0, 82, 255);padding: 6px 0px 0px 6px;box-shadow: rgba(220, 254, 255, 0.2) 6px 6px 0px 0px;margin: -29px 7px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding:15px 25px 30px 23px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: flex-start;margin-top: 10px;\">\n       <div data-autoskip=\"1\" style=\"background:none;letter-spacing:1.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\">\n        <div data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"4EZlweZ08EVRzqxA\" data-pm-slice=\"4 4 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;4ever-article&quot;,&quot;data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key&quot;:&quot;4EZlweZ08EVRzqxA&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;_135editor active&quot;,&quot;data-tools&quot;:&quot;135编辑器&quot;,&quot;data-id&quot;:&quot;136445&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 10px auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;border-radius: 0; padding: 25px; background-color: #f0f4ff; box-sizing: border-box; opacity: 1;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-autoskip&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;135brush styleActive&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify; line-height:1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size:14px; color:#333333; background: transparent;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">\n         <div data-clipboard-cangjie=\"[&quot;root&quot;,{},[&quot;p&quot;,{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;mechatgrwyu747dwl1&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;leaf&quot;},&quot;🔥 这个夏天，开源热潮比气温更燃！Qwen3、GLM4.5、混元、Wan2.2、Qwen-Image等重磅模型密集发布，MoE、多模态、Agent、生图视频全爆发，ModelScope 全程 Day0 支持，生态持续进化中！&quot;]]],[&quot;p&quot;,{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;mechatgsioh28q7nasp&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;leaf&quot;},&quot;&quot;]]],[&quot;p&quot;,{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;mechatgsrlpwct1ljor&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;leaf&quot;},&quot;💻 从以图搜图、MCP升级到API兼容，魔搭持续优化全链路体验，线上线下联动开发者，一起共建更开放、更强大的AI未来！&quot;]]]]\" data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"8oLl952PM7wjdlap\">\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">今天是 10 月 24 日「程序员节」。在这个属于开发者的日子里，魔搭社区联合知乎发布首份聚焦AI时代开发者的重磅报告——《THE NEXT WAVE：AI时代开发者生态白皮书》。</span></span></p>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">这份报告尝试回答一个问题——在AI时代，我们应如何更完整地理解「开发者」？</span></span></p>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">报告告诉我们：AI 把“会写代码”的门槛拉低，却把一个更稀缺的角色推上前台——能定义问题、选技术、闭环商业的「超级个体」开发者。</span></span></p>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">他们长什么样？怎么想？又怎么做？</span></span></p>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 4 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:17px;\">画像：经验与活力并存，规模不再分大小&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n          <ul style=\"font-size: 14px;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n           <li>\n            <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">年龄：28-32 岁最多，33-37 岁占 22%，23-27 岁占 20%。&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n           </li>\n          </ul>\n          <ul style=\"font-size: 14px;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n           <li>\n            <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">学历：93.35% 本科及以上，集中在互联网/软件（50.7%）和 AI（32.7%）。&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n           </li>\n          </ul>\n          <ul style=\"font-size: 14px;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n           <li>\n            <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">组织：大厂 24.27%，50 人以下小团队 20.74%，独立开发者 13.7%。&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n           </li>\n          </ul>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">工具平权让“单枪匹马”也敢上场。</span></span></p>\n          <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"91330\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n           <div style=\"margin: 10px auto;\">\n            <div data-role=\"animate\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;overflow-x: auto;max-width: 100% !important;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-width=\"100%\">\n             <div data-divisor=\"1\" style=\"overflow: hidden;width: 200%;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 200% !important;\" data-width=\"200%\">\n              <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 50%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-width=\"50%\">\n               <div style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n                <p style=\"vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;max-width: 100% !important;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-width=\"100%\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"AI时代开发者白皮书_知乎&amp;魔搭_页面_16.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" title=\"undefined\" data-width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"100017999\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8b546a24&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHytN6OfQHzVlsbs8iaISlcZXZOzpHLb0SxDDk9mC3dCZUmlqlyDVpkgOsDjXd7KlOYuhEe5CicfjG53xZiaUBcHqA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n               </div>\n              </div>\n              <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 50%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-width=\"50%\">\n               <div style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n                <p style=\"vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;max-width: 100% !important;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-width=\"100%\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" title=\"undefined\" data-width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"100018000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3ce5e58e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHytN6OfQHzVlsbs8iaISlcZXZOzpHLb0Sy3QamWcSyqNyOKXloKaCvtB6FibTHbUXvauzVOwzpK7Ia7LXrcCw7PQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n               </div>\n              </div>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n             <p style=\"line-height:32px;margin: 10px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">左右滑动查看更多</span></span></p>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 4 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:17px;\">认知：最怕的不是失业，是「用不起来」&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n          <ul style=\"font-size: 14px;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n           <li>\n            <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">仅三成担心被 AI 取代；79.4% 焦虑“如何把 AI 变业务价值”，60.8% 焦虑“技术更新太快”。&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n           </li>\n           <li>\n            <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">入行动机：63.55% 是对前沿技术的热情，59.11% 想抓时代机遇，25.62% 才是高收入。&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n           </li>\n          </ul>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">一句话：他们把 AI 当杠杆，而非对手。</span></span></p>\n          <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"91330\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n           <div style=\"margin: 10px auto;\">\n            <div data-role=\"animate\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;overflow-x: auto;max-width: 100% !important;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-width=\"100%\">\n             <div data-divisor=\"1\" style=\"overflow: hidden;width: 200%;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 200% !important;\" data-width=\"200%\">\n              <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 50%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-width=\"50%\">\n               <div style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n                <p style=\"vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;max-width: 100% !important;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-width=\"100%\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"AI时代开发者白皮书_知乎&amp;魔搭_页面_20.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017997\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"100%\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" title=\"undefined\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2681a2b4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHytN6OfQHzVlsbs8iaISlcZXZOzpHLb0S5gd0rYKCh7oYStTkl5Hic8ic0KMfpCVrtpwzYks7xaK7x68Bk6decrOw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n               </div>\n              </div>\n              <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 50%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-width=\"50%\">\n               <div style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n                <p style=\"vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;max-width: 100% !important;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-width=\"100%\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017998\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"100%\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" title=\"undefined\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5f090cc2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHytN6OfQHzVlsbs8iaISlcZXZOzpHLb0Sicia5Q15icNtWUc45dFFz1FVyPpk021EKDkJaIKA8I1mwuWKK8B69OQfA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n               </div>\n              </div>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n             <p style=\"line-height:32px;margin: 10px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">左右滑动查看更多</span></span></p>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <p style=\"padding-top:0px;text-indent:0em;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;padding-bottom:0px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">行为：从“写代码”到“搭系统”&nbsp;</span></p>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">能力杠杆&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">产品经理用 Cursor 两天做出可交互 Demo，“做 Demo 比画原型更快”。&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">前特斯拉后端工程师靠 AI 写 100% 代码，一年上线 4 款 App。&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">认知飞轮&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">感知 → 溯源（官网/论文） → 消化（知乎多元讨论） → 应用。&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">知乎 7 年以上用户中，78% 已从读者变创作者。&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 4 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">实践飞轮&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 4 []\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">魔搭提供 12 万+ 模型、5500+ MCP 服务，像乐高一样组合产生应用；魔搭</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">创空间已诞生 2.3 万个应用，95% 出自个人开发者，覆盖 20 多个行业。</span></p>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当认知场降低理解成本，实践场降低实现成本，“一个人+AI”正在逼近过去“一个小团队”的交付半径。</span></span></p>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017994\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b2e1f97c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHytN6OfQHzVlsbs8iaISlcZXZOzpHLb0SMcycV0TRQSbX56IqmL0xbdZyZbXSAngyZO8SzgtIYUeEiaJjnw141pw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">「超级个体」开发者不是新工具的产物，而是新身份的起点——更自主、更全能、更能闭环。</span></span></p>\n          <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\">完整开发者白皮书，点击</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">阅读原文</span><span textstyle=\"\">查看下载</span></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "白皮书摘要揭示 AI 时代开发者正向“超级个体”演进，具备定义问题、技术选型和商业闭环能力。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "白皮书摘要揭示 AI 时代开发者正向“超级个体”演进，具备定义问题、技术选型和商业闭环能力。",
  "summary": "文章是知乎与魔搭社区联合发布的《AI 时代开发者生态白皮书》的摘要。它重新定义了 AI 时代的开发者，指出 AI 虽降低了编程门槛，却催生了能定义问题、选择技术并实现商业闭环的“超级个体”。报告通过开发者画像（年龄、学历、组织规模）、认知（不惧失业，但焦虑 AI 业务价值转化和技术更新速度）和行为（从“写代码”到“搭系统”，利用 AI 作为能力杠杆和认知飞轮）三个维度，描绘了这一新角色的特征。文章强调，AI 赋能个人开发者，使其交付能力逼近小团队，预示着开发者将变得更自主、全能和能闭环。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 降低编程门槛，催生了具备全栈商业闭环能力的“超级个体”开发者。",
      "explanation": "传统编码技能不再是唯一核心，AI 赋能开发者将重心转向问题定义、技术选型与商业价值实现，形成更自主、全能的新型个体。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 时代开发者更关注如何将 AI 转化为业务价值，而非被 AI 取代。",
      "explanation": "报告显示开发者主要焦虑如何应用 AI 创造商业价值及应对技术快速迭代，而非担忧失业，视 AI 为提升效率的工具。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 作为能力杠杆和认知飞轮，赋能个人开发者实现小团队的交付能力。",
      "explanation": "借助 AI 工具与平台，个人开发者能高效完成过去需团队协作的任务，降低了理解与实现成本，加速了应用创新与交付。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "AI 把\"会写代码\"的门槛拉低，却把一个更稀缺的角色推上前台——能定义问题、选技术、闭环商业的「超级个体」开发者。",
    "他们把 AI 当杠杆，而非对手。",
    "当认知场降低理解成本，实践场降低实现成本，'一个人+AI'正在逼近过去'一个小团队'的交付半径。",
    "「超级个体」开发者不是新工具的产物，而是新身份的起点——更自主、更全能、更能闭环。"
  ],
